org.osate.aadl2

Interface ProcessImplementation

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AObject, Classifier, ComponentClassifier, ComponentImplementation, Element, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, FeatureClassifier, org.eclipse.core.runtime.IAdaptable, NamedElement, Namespace, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Process, ProcessClassifier, ProcessSubcomponentType, SubcomponentType, Type
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ProcessImplementationImpl

    public interface ProcessImplementation
extends ComponentImplementation, ProcessClassifier
    A representation of the model object 'Process Implementation'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Owned Data Subcomponent
    • Owned Subprogram Subcomponent
    • Owned Subprogram Group Subcomponent
    • Owned Thread Subcomponent
    • Owned Thread Group Subcomponent
